name: AceWeaR STARS
description: The second conception for Conflict Design. The "Stars" Tee had been picked up overseas as the "it" apparel to go with your Chucks© For some reason they cannot get enough of the similarity to the Converse© logo. So whether you just wanna be up on the latest trend or just like the Tee for other reasons Stars is just another design masterpiece from Conflict. This shirt actually retails at $49.99 in the United States but for a short time we are launching them at the low price of $29.99.

name: AceWeaR ANGEL
description: The very first conception for Conflict Design. The "Angel" Tee has been the companies best seller for a very long time and it's easy to see why! Boasting a set of glowing wings positioned over your shoulders (authentic to a real angel) who wouldn't want this one of a kind masterpiece? This shirt actually retails at $49.99 in the United States but for a short time we are launching them at the low price of $29.99.

name: AceWeaR RAINBOW
description: The fourth conception for Conflict Design. The "Rainbow" Tee screams attitude. Not the kind you get with several holes in your face but definitely a pain-free alternative. This shirt looks kickass in combination with a good hoodie :) This shirt actually retails at $49.99 in the United States but for a short time we are launching them at the low price of $29.99.

name: AceWeaR FAMOUS
description:
The third conception for Conflict Design.

The "Famous" Tee. What is there left to say? This tee embodies everything that is Conflict Design in it's grass roots. Pretty much ladies and gents grab our gear before it ends up on rodeo drive @ a few hundred dollars a pop ;) Sporting a special Gold Glitter Flex this tee sparkles like a set of fifty's grillz!

This shirt actually retails at $49.99 in the United States but for a short time we are launching them at the low price of $29.99.
